narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: It's not the gut language. But it is really fun, and I found it an enjoyable way to fulfill my L1 req.
A good intro language course. Can be a lot of work though some days with weekly essays.

If you have not taken Italian, I think this introductory class is the way to go. I know that there is an accelerated class, but I thought that this class moved at a great pace, and any faster would have ben overwhelming. The class is focused on grammar and learning basic vocabulary. I would recommend this class to another student.
